  "content": [
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "1. Open chery 8255 Software Req_Cart and add module explorer widget"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "here is the link below:"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "https://rb-alm-20-p.de.bosch.com/rm/web#action=com.ibm.rdm.web.pages.showArtifactPage&artifactURI=https%3A%2F%2Frb-alm-20-p.de.bosch.com%2Frm%2Fresources%2FMD_EBI2qx5QEe-KXae95JKs7A&artifactInModule=https%3A%2F%2Frb-alm-20-p.de.bosch.com%2Frm%2Fresources%2FBI_EBSntR5QEe-KXae95JKs7A&componentURI=https%3A%2F%2Frb-alm-20-p.de.bosch.com%2Frm%2Frm-projects%2F_8HIsAOK7Ee6XXvwUSNli6A%2Fcomponents%2F_8aqE8OK7Ee6XXvwUSNli6A&vvc.configuration=https%3A%2F%2Frb-alm-20-p.de.bosch.com%2Frm%2Fcm%2Fstream%2F_8a8_5uK7Ee6XXvwUSNli6A"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Add module explorer to dashboard, so we can find specific SM easily"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/How%20to%20get%20dng%20link%20and%20modify%20UDS%20md%20file/image-2024-6-12_9-36-5.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/How to get dng link and modify UDS md file/image-2024-6-12_9-36-5.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "2. Save htm file to get link"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Go to a SM module, you can add some attributions in column,  and save the file as htm format.  Here is an example for SM13:"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/How%20to%20get%20dng%20link%20and%20modify%20UDS%20md%20file/image-2024-6-12_10-47-27.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/How to get dng link and modify UDS md file/image-2024-6-12_10-47-27.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/How%20to%20get%20dng%20link%20and%20modify%20UDS%20md%20file/image-2024-6-12_9-42-30.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/How to get dng link and modify UDS md file/image-2024-6-12_9-42-30.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Download .py file to generate the links of SWRS-HLR-xxx, put this python file in the folder where you save the htm file"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "getLink.py"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Run .py file"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "PS: this script is just a frame, you may modify it depending on the format of your htm file."
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/How%20to%20get%20dng%20link%20and%20modify%20UDS%20md%20file/image-2024-6-12_10-39-19.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/How to get dng link and modify UDS md file/image-2024-6-12_10-39-19.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "3. Modify md file"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Open md file in below path:"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/How%20to%20get%20dng%20link%20and%20modify%20UDS%20md%20file/image-2024-6-12_10-43-59.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/How to get dng link and modify UDS md file/image-2024-6-12_10-43-59.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Update dng file and SWRS_HLR- number in md file"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/How%20to%20get%20dng%20link%20and%20modify%20UDS%20md%20file/image-2024-6-12_10-45-31.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/How to get dng link and modify UDS md file/image-2024-6-12_10-45-31.png"
    }
